/*********************************************/
*
* libitm is originally downloaded from:
*
* gcc 4.7.2/libitm
*
/*********************************************/

NOTE of what you would probably need to do:

1. modify libitm as you wish
2. make
3. don't forget to do *make install*
4. make sure LD_LIBRARY_PATH has been set correctly.
   e.g. should include ${destdir}/lib, lib32 and lib64
5. test your gcc, use ITM_DEFAULT_METHOD to specify a TM alg
